snippet.title: Diwali Special Laxmi Aarti by Anuradha Paudwal | Om Jai Laxmi Mata | लक्ष्मीजी की आरती हिंदी
snippet.description:
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata is one of the most famous Aarti of Maa Lakshmi. This famous Aarti of Lakshmi Mata is recited on most occasions related to Lakshmi Mata.

Singer: Anuradha Paudwal
Music Director: Sanjayraj Gaurinandan (SRG)
Lyrics: Traditional

Om Jai Lakshmi Mata,Maiya Jai Lakshmi Mata।
Tumako Nishidin Sevat,Hari Vishnu Vidhata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥
Uma Rama Brahmani,Tum Hi Jag-Mata।
Surya-Chandrama DhyavatNaarad Rishi Gata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥
Durga Roop Niranjani,Sukh Sampatti Data।
Jo Koi Tumako Dhyavat,Riddhi-Siddhi Dhan Pata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥
Tum Patal-Nivasini,Tum Hi Shubhdata।
Karma-Prabhav-Prakashini,Bhavanidhi Ki Trata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥
Jis Ghar Mein Tum Rahti,Sab Sadgun Aata।

snippet.title: Diwali Special Aarti : ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता Om Jai Laxmi Mata Aarti : लक्ष्मी जी की आरती : Laxmi Aarti
snippet.description:
Diwali Special Aarti : ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता Om Jai Laxmi Mata Aarti : लक्ष्मी जी की आरती : Laxmi Aarti
Diwali Special Aarti : ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता Om Jai Laxmi Mata Aarti : लक्ष्मी जी की आरती : Laxmi Aarti
Diwali Special Aarti : ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता Om Jai Laxmi Mata Aarti : लक्ष्मी जी की आरती : Laxmi Aarti

#laxmiaarti #diwalispecial #lakshmiaarti

Aarti Laxmi Mata Lyrics :

ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता, मैया जय लक्ष्मी माता।
तुमको निशिदिन सेवत, हरि विष्णु विधाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

उमा, रमा, ब्रह्माणी, तुम ही जग-माता।
सूर्य-चन्द्रमा ध्यावत, नारद ऋषि गाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

दुर्गा रुप निरंजनी, सुख सम्पत्ति दाता।
जो कोई तुमको ध्यावत, ऋद्धि-सिद्धि धन पाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

तुम पाताल-निवासिनि, तुम ही शुभदाता।
कर्म-प्रभाव-प्रकाशिनी, भवनिधि की त्राता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

जिस घर में तुम रहतीं, सब सद्गुण आता।
सब सम्भव हो जाता, मन नहीं घबराता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

तुम बिन यज्ञ न होते, वस्त्र न कोई पाता।
खान-पान का वैभव, सब तुमसे आता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

शुभ-गुण मन्दिर सुन्दर, क्षीरोदधि-जाता।
रत्न चतुर्दश तुम बिन, कोई नहीं पाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

महालक्ष्मीजी की आरती, जो कोई जन गाता।
उर आनन्द समाता, पाप उतर जाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

Om Jai Laxmi Mata Lyrics in English :

Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Maiya Jai Lakshmi Mata।
Tumako Nishidin Sevat, Hari Vishnu Vidhata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Uma Rama Brahmani, Tum Hi Jag-Mata।
Surya-Chandrama Dhyavat Naarad Rishi Gata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Durga Roop Niranjani, Sukh Sampatti Data।
Jo Koi Tumako Dhyavat, Riddhi-Siddhi Dhan Pata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Tum Patal-Nivasini, Tum Hi Shubhdata।
Karma-Prabhav-Prakashini, Bhavanidhi Ki Trata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Jis Ghar Mein Tum Rahti, Sab Sadgun Aata।
Sab Sambhav Ho Jata, Man Nahi Ghabrata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

#laxmiaarti #diwalispecial #lakshmiaarti

Aarti Laxmi Mata Lyrics :

ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता, मैया जय लक्ष्मी माता।
तुमको निशिदिन सेवत, हरि विष्णु विधाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

उमा, रमा, ब्रह्माणी, तुम ही जग-माता।
सूर्य-चन्द्रमा ध्यावत, नारद ऋषि गाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

दुर्गा रुप निरंजनी, सुख सम्पत्ति दाता।
जो कोई तुमको ध्यावत, ऋद्धि-सिद्धि धन पाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

तुम पाताल-निवासिनि, तुम ही शुभदाता।
कर्म-प्रभाव-प्रकाशिनी, भवनिधि की त्राता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

जिस घर में तुम रहतीं, सब सद्गुण आता।
सब सम्भव हो जाता, मन नहीं घबराता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

तुम बिन यज्ञ न होते, वस्त्र न कोई पाता।
खान-पान का वैभव, सब तुमसे आता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

शुभ-गुण मन्दिर सुन्दर, क्षीरोदधि-जाता।
रत्न चतुर्दश तुम बिन, कोई नहीं पाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

महालक्ष्मीजी की आरती, जो कोई जन गाता।
उर आनन्द समाता, पाप उतर जाता॥
ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता॥

Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Maiya Jai Lakshmi Mata।
Tumako Nishidin Sevat, Hari Vishnu Vidhata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Uma Rama Brahmani, Tum Hi Jag-Mata।
Surya-Chandrama Dhyavat Naarad Rishi Gata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Durga Roop Niranjani, Sukh Sampatti Data।
Jo Koi Tumako Dhyavat, Riddhi-Siddhi Dhan Pata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Tum Patal-Nivasini, Tum Hi Shubhdata।
Karma-Prabhav-Prakashini, Bhavanidhi Ki Trata॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Jis Ghar Mein Tum Rahti, Sab Sadgun Aata।

Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

Om Jai Lakshmi Mata॥

snippet.title: Celebrating Maria Tallchief
snippet.description:
In honor of Native American Heritage Month in the U.S., today’s video Doodle—created in partnership with Native American guest artists Lydia Cheshewalla, Chris Pappan, and Yatika Starr Fields— celebrates Maria Tallchief, member of the Osage Nation who was America’s first, major prima ballerina. Not only a trailblazer for Native American dancers, Tallchief is widely considered one of the country’s most influential ballerinas of all time. On this day in 2007, a bronze sculpture of Tallchief and four other Native American ballerinas was unveiled in Oklahoma at the Tulsa Historical Society in a piece titled “The Five Moons” by artist Gary Henson. 

Learn more: http://www.google.com/doodles/celebrating-maria-tallchief

-------

Quote by Maria Tallchief is an excerpt of Bruce Duffie's published interview with Maria Tallchief: "Conversation Piece: Prima Ballerina MARIA TALLCHIEF" © Bruce Duffie

snippet.title: Donald Trump motorcade drives by supporters protesting US election results
snippet.description:
Donald Trump's motorcade drove past supporters protesting the US election results on Saturday. 
Trump was on his way to a nearby golf course in northern Virginia when he reportedly intentionally chose the route. He passed his supporters in Washington DC demonstrating against the results of the presidential election, which Joe Biden won. 
Pro-Trump demonstrations are scheduled to take place across the US on 14 November, with counter protests also planned

snippet.title: CLAN WARS 2 IMPROVEMENTS & FIXES! 🛠️ Clash Royale Update TV Royale
snippet.description:
We heard your Clan Wars 2 feedback! We're adding a number of new changes and improvements to the Clan Wars experience in our next update. Follow Drew on Twitter: https://twitter.com/drewbian
Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

00:00 TIME ZONE ISSUE
00:47 PARTICPATION CAP
01:05 CLAN MATCHMAKING
01:44 NEW RIVER LENGTHS
02:07 FAME BOOST
02:21 GAME MODES

02:47 CLAN UI CHANGES
03:22 NEW MINIMUM MEMBER CAP
03:36 SUPERCELL ID FRIENDS
03:57 OTHER FIXES & IMPROVEMENTS

Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more.

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

Lead the Clash Royale Family to victory!

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

snippet.title: Behind the Doodle: Celebrating Maria Tallchief
snippet.description:
In honor of Native American Heritage Month in the U.S., today’s video Doodle—created in partnership with Native American guest artists Lydia Cheshewalla, Chris Pappan, and Yatika Starr Fields— celebrates Maria Tallchief, member of the Osage Nation who was America’s first, major prima ballerina. Not only a trailblazer for Native American dancers, Tallchief is widely considered one of the country’s most influential ballerinas of all time. On this day in 2007, a bronze sculpture of Tallchief and four other Native American ballerinas was unveiled in Oklahoma at the Tulsa Historical Society in a piece titled “The Five Moons” by artist Gary Henson. 

Learn more: http://www.google.com/doodles/celebrating-maria-tallchief

The Firebird, Swan Lake and The Nutcracker: "Dance of the Sugar Plum Fairy", Choreography by George Balanchine © The George Balanchine Trust

-------

snippet.title: Fixing The UNFIXABLE: Squishy Makeovers from "The Hopeless Bin"
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Today I am doing a video that was honestly DEMANDED by some people in my comment sections recently 😂 Many of you really wanted to see my attempt to "Fix The Unfixable," sooooo, here I go. This special episode of squishy makeovers will be me attempting to fix and redecorate squishies from the WORST or worst. These extremely damaged squishies come from my "hopeless bin" and I was honestly not sure if they would ever make it out!
Also, I am aware that this whole "spamming" of my comment setions kind of started a war between those who were doing it and those who thought it was really annoying 😂 I appreciate those of you who didn't want me to be pressured into doing a video I didn't want to do! Don't worry, I'm happy to give it a try. And I appreciate getting video requests from you guys.

DON'T FORGET ABOUT THE COUSIN DERP PLUSH!
https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

AND The new Christmas apparel design is now available here:
https://moriah-elizabeth.teespring.com/listing/special-holiday-collection?product=345


_________FAQs__________

1. CAN I SEND YOU SQUISHIES?
So many generous people have sent me their unwanted squishies so I actually have a lot to work on already, BUT if you desperately want to, you can request my mailing address in the email ALLLL the way at down in the description (sorry for the traveling), make sure to read the disclaimer down there as well.

2. ARE SQUISHIES RETURNED TO THE SENDERS AFTER THE MAKEOVER?
No. These squishies  are sent as donations to the series because they were damaged, and no longer wanted. Everyone has been informed in advance that squishies would not be returned. It would be waaay too complicated/expensive and massively time consuming to keep track of everyone and return each squishy. I'm just one person! 

3. WHAT PAINT DO YOU USE?
I use fabric paint. Fabric paint is meant to stretch, so it is perfect for squishing! Any brand will work fine, but I mainly use Tulip. You can find it at Michaels, Hobby Lobby, A.C. Moore, Walmart, Joann Fabrics, and Online.

5. WILL FABRIC PAINT CRACK?
The matte fabric paint is more likely to crack after lots of squishing. Slick fabric paints never crack. But there are benefits to both. I usually mix the two paints together to get the best of both worlds.


___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh 😂 ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating, painting and general art videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers

Craft Kit Testing: pretty self explanatory. testing craft kits.

snippet.title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 3 FULL Breakdown (Big Episode)
snippet.description:
The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 3 was my favourite episode yet. 
Spoilers!!

Bringing in Bo Katan into this episode was incredible. Katee Sackhoff did an outstanding job as playing Bo Katan (who she voices in The Clone Wars and Rebels). I can't wait to see the next episode and hopefully Ahsoka Tano played by Rosario Dawson! There were tons of important things in this episode that I hope to breakdown with you.

Something super important to mention is that Bo says Din Djarin is a child of the watch, children of the watch are a cult of religious zealots who broke away from mandalorian society, their goal is to re-establish the ancient way she’s talking about death watch who were the ones who saved him as a kid.

Death watch were hellbent on making Mandalore what it once was, they were very purist and elitist and led by Pre Vizsla  during the Clone Wars who died to Darth Maul in trial by combat. Maul had the dark sober and Bo Katan and the other members of clan Kryze were pushed out.

She says that Mandalorians are stronger when together, and he says it’s not part of his plan, as he’s been quested to bringing this child to the Jedi. Bo says she knows of one she can introduce him to, if he helps them with their mission (Ahsoka Tano).

We see an awesome few minutes of pure action where the 4 Mandalorians make stormtroopers look like…well…stormtroopers.

Now in regards to the Dark Saber for those who need a quick recap -  The dark saber is basically the Key to uniting Mandalore and the Mandalorian people. Think of the Dark Saber as a key to the planet. Whoever possesses it, rules Mandalore. The only way to take it, is to kill the possessor of the blade, or challenge them to a trial by combat, like Maul did to Pre Viszla. 
So it makes me wonder how Giddeon did it to Bo, did he take it from her, if so then how is she alive? 

At the end of Rebels, Sabine gave the saber to Bo to take back Mandalore under her rule, so the gap has yet to be filled in. As they move their way up to the bridge, Moff Gideon talks to the captain via holo, where he learns that it’s the Mandalorians who have attacked the Empire’s other vessels, calling them, pirates.

I'm excited to know what Ahsoka Tano is up to. Has she had any kind of communication with Anakin Skywalker in the force now that he's a ghost again?

Bringing in Bo Katan into this episode was incredible. Katee Sackhoff did an outstanding job as playing Bo Katan (who she voices in The Clone Wars and Rebels). I can't wait to see the next episode and hopefully Ahsoka Tano played by Rosario Dawson! There were tons of important things in this episode that I hope to breakdown with you.

Something super important to mention is that Bo says Din Djarin is a child of the watch, children of the watch are a cult of religious zealots who broke away from mandalorian society, their goal is to re-establish the ancient way she’s talking about death watch who were the ones who saved him as a kid.

Death watch were hellbent on making Mandalore what it once was, they were very purist and elitist and led by Pre Vizsla  during the Clone Wars who died to Darth Maul in trial by combat. Maul had the dark sober and Bo Katan and the other members of clan Kryze were pushed out.

She says that Mandalorians are stronger when together, and he says it’s not part of his plan, as he’s been quested to bringing this child to the Jedi. Bo says she knows of one she can introduce him to, if he helps them with their mission (Ahsoka Tano).

We see an awesome few minutes of pure action where the 4 Mandalorians make stormtroopers look like…well…stormtroopers.

Now in regards to the Dark Saber for those who need a quick recap -  The dark saber is basically the Key to uniting Mandalore and the Mandalorian people. Think of the Dark Saber as a key to the planet. Whoever possesses it, rules Mandalore. The only way to take it, is to kill the possessor of the blade, or challenge them to a trial by combat, like Maul did to Pre Viszla. 
So it makes me wonder how Giddeon did it to Bo, did he take it from her, if so then how is she alive? 

At the end of Rebels, Sabine gave the saber to Bo to take back Mandalore under her rule, so the gap has yet to be filled in. As they move their way up to the bridge, Moff Gideon talks to the captain via holo, where he learns that it’s the Mandalorians who have attacked the Empire’s other vessels, calling them, pirates.

I'm excited to know what Ahsoka Tano is up to. Has she had any kind of communication with Anakin Skywalker in the force now that he's a ghost again?

snippet.title: Lidl | Big on a Christmas you can believe in (2020)
snippet.description:
Could a friendship be ahead? No. It’s a Christmas ad for Lidl with great prices instead! 

The world is hushed and white with snow,
Lonely hearts meet through a window.
Could a friendship be ahead?
No it’s a Christmas ad from Lidl with great prices instead.

Free range British turkey, smell the magic,
A jumper with our logo and a pig in a blanket.
Great value parsnips, oh what a price!
Emotional gravy, that potato looks nice.

We don’t need cutesy characters when carrots taste this good.
We don’t want romance, we want award winning Christmas pud.

There’s usually a moment where we want you to feel sad…
But we don’t have time, look sparkling wine!
This cheese will make you feel so glad.
Proper Christmas magic is in cake and sprouts and gin.
At Lidl we’re Big on a Christmas you can believe in.

#BigOnLidlChristmas

snippet.title: Christmas 2020 Ad | Give A Little Love | Waitrose & John Lewis
snippet.description:
We believe that the world would be a better place if we all gave a little more love.  So this year we're celebrating kindness, whether large or small, showing how each and every act of love has a positive impact on the world around us, as we pass them on to others.  

Together with Waitrose & Partners we're hoping to raise £4m for our charities plus £1m for local charities. FareShare, helps those facing food poverty, and Home-Start, which works with parents who need support ❤️.  The charities will use these donations to provide food, comfort, emotional support and advice to families who need support this Christmas.

Watch the ad with audio description here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=No1qinjBNrw

snippet.title: food fight
snippet.description:
juicy youtooz giveaway: http://icecreamsandwich.youtooz.com/ 
OOOOHHHH 2 VIDEOS IN LESS THAN 28 DAYS????
HOW DID HE DO IT??? ˢˡᵉᵉᵖ ᵈᵉᵖʳᶦᵛᵃᵗᶦᵒⁿ

This video was about a food fight I experienced back in jr high school. It was uneventful but eventful at the same time. More chaos than food fight if I'm honest. But you probably already know that because who reads the description before watching the video am I right.

It was a bad time because we got punished in an intense way, but it was also a good time because it was really crazy to be a part of. School isn't always that great so to be able to spice things up with U̴̡̧̕N̵̩̠̓́R̶̰̪̒Ė̶̘̟L̸̙̤̿E̸̜͖͌N̴̦̪̈́T̵͗̔͜Ĩ̷͙͊N̸͍̞̎G̴͉̯̊̑ ̶̣̈́D̷͉͐Ĕ̴̱͋S̸̨̰̿̋T̴̙̲̋R̵̮̩̐̓Ú̸͕̊C̴͇̹̓T̶̙̏̔ͅĬ̷̤Ô̵̡̰͘N̸̞̊ ̶̝̦͆́Â̵̮͚͋N̷͉̓D̷̳͉̏ ̷̡̿C̷̘̿H̵̘̖̐A̶̠̅O̷̧̓S̶͔̽ is a fun way to keep things interesting. If you're in high school or whatever try D̷͕̒I̵̡͙̎S̷̳̝̐M̸̤͕̆A̴̟̙̒͑N̷̐̍ͅT̸͓̽̈L̴̞̜̔Ị̷̾͊Ņ̷̌͝ͅḠ̵̣̱ ̴͈̠͒̇T̵̬̳̽͘H̷̦͗̃Ë̶͎̣́̽ ̴̭̹̒S̸̖͑Y̸̳͋̈S̴̺̳̾̿T̸̢̲̓E̴̯̒M̶͖̙̍͝ to get through the day it might be fun.

I also partnered with youtooz to create a little icecreamsandwich figurine. I talk about it at the end of the video. If you follow me outside of youtube you probably know that by know. It's exciting actually it turned out great. I hope you like it too!

Oh also I am starting another channel to put my short animations on. Usually I post them to tiktok or instagram or twitter but I think putting them on youtube. It might be the main home for them in the future. I'm still working on setting it up so things might change. 
Check it out here if you're in to that kind of thing: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6KVHFHpCwujbw2TfKnQ3uQ

thanks for watching ❤️ see you next video.

snippet.title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 3 FULL Breakdown (Big Episode)
snippet.description:
The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 3 was my favourite episode yet. 
Spoilers!!

Bringing in Bo Katan into this episode was incredible. Katee Sackhoff did an outstanding job as playing Bo Katan (who she voices in The Clone Wars and Rebels). I can't wait to see the next episode and hopefully Ahsoka Tano played by Rosario Dawson! There were tons of important things in this episode that I hope to breakdown with you.

Something super important to mention is that Bo says Din Djarin is a child of the watch, children of the watch are a cult of religious zealots who broke away from mandalorian society, their goal is to re-establish the ancient way she’s talking about death watch who were the ones who saved him as a kid.

Death watch were hellbent on making Mandalore what it once was, they were very purist and elitist and led by Pre Vizsla  during the Clone Wars who died to Darth Maul in trial by combat. Maul had the dark sober and Bo Katan and the other members of clan Kryze were pushed out.

She says that Mandalorians are stronger when together, and he says it’s not part of his plan, as he’s been quested to bringing this child to the Jedi. Bo says she knows of one she can introduce him to, if he helps them with their mission (Ahsoka Tano).

We see an awesome few minutes of pure action where the 4 Mandalorians make stormtroopers look like…well…stormtroopers.

Now in regards to the Dark Saber for those who need a quick recap -  The dark saber is basically the Key to uniting Mandalore and the Mandalorian people. Think of the Dark Saber as a key to the planet. Whoever possesses it, rules Mandalore. The only way to take it, is to kill the possessor of the blade, or challenge them to a trial by combat, like Maul did to Pre Viszla. 
So it makes me wonder how Giddeon did it to Bo, did he take it from her, if so then how is she alive? 

At the end of Rebels, Sabine gave the saber to Bo to take back Mandalore under her rule, so the gap has yet to be filled in. As they move their way up to the bridge, Moff Gideon talks to the captain via holo, where he learns that it’s the Mandalorians who have attacked the Empire’s other vessels, calling them, pirates.

I'm excited to know what Ahsoka Tano is up to. Has she had any kind of communication with Anakin Skywalker in the force now that he's a ghost again?

曾偉權病逝終年58歲 好友文雪兒感惋惜

據報入行逾40年嘅資深演員 #曾偉權 病逝，終年58歲。曾偉權患病嘅傳聞自年前已經傳出，之後佢就深居簡出，同外界朋友斷絕聯絡。11月中傳出佢病危留院，最終不敵病魔與世長辭。

入行多年嘅佢演出經驗豐富，亦曾為多間電視台效力，近年嘅《牛下女高音》可以話係佢得意之作，又有參予《法證先鋒IV》同《使徒行者3》，之後即為休養而停工休息。

#曾偉權 #病逝 #回顧

snippet.title: Live coverage: Joe Biden wins presidency, CBS News projects
snippet.description:
CBS News projects Joe Biden has secured enough electoral votes to become the 46th president of the United States, defeating President Trump and capturing the White House after a bitter campaign that exposed deep divides in the country.

President-elect Biden and Vice President-elect Kamala Harris are delivering remarks in Wilmington, Delaware, after their projected victory at 8 p.m. ET.

#JoeBiden #2020Election #PresidentialElection

CBSN is CBS News’ 24/7 digital streaming news service featuring live, anchored coverage available for free across all platforms. Launched in November 2014, the service is a premier destination for breaking news and original storytelling from the deep bench of CBS News correspondents and reporters. CBSN features the top stories of the day as well as deep dives into key issues facing the nation and the world. CBSN has also expanded to launch local news streaming services in major markets across the country. CBSN is currently available on CBSNews.com and the CBS News app across more than 20 platforms, as well as the CBS All Access subscription service.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Arsenal vs Aston Villa (0-3) | Premier League
snippet.description:
We were well-beaten by Aston Villa on a deeply disappointing night at Emirates Stadium on Sunday.
 
Coming into the game on the back of a morale-boosting win at Old Trafford, hopes were high but the visitors immediately underlined their attacking intent when, just seconds into the match, John McGinn swept the ball into the top corner.
 
Villa celebrated wildly, but the decision was checked by VAR – and the ‘goal’ ruled out as Ross Barkley was offside and adjudged to be impeding the view of Bernd Leno as McGinn struck the ball.
 
It was a major let-off for us, but we struggled to impose ourselves for much of the first half – although Willian blazed one effort over the bar after good work by Thomas Partey and Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang.
 
But it was the visitors who took the lead when Matt Targett swept the ball across the face of goal and it was bundled in off the unfortunate Bukayo Saka.
 
We responded positively and had a golden chance to equalise when Kieran Tierney’s pinpoint cross from the left picked out Alex Lacazette, but the forward could not keep his header down.
 
It was a disappointing end to a disappointing half, but after the restart it was the visitors who were first to threaten again, with Bernd Leno forced to palm away Trezeguet’s shot.
 
Jack Grealish then came close to extending Villa’s advantage from close range, only to see his curling effort deflected behind - before Rob Holding fired wide at the other end.
 
Nicolas Pepe and Eddie Nketiah were soon thrown into the fray as we looked for a way back into the game, with the former coming close with a fine curling effort.
 
But Villa’s fluent attacking display was rewarded with a second goal when Douglas Luiz found Barkley at the back post, and his volleyed cross was headed in by Ollie Watkins.
 
The Villa striker then made it three moments later to compound a miserable night for us at Emirates Stadium.
 
#arsenal #premierleague

snippet.title: Syamel, Elly Mazlein, Zizi Kirana, Faizal Tahir - Salahku, 4 Dara | #ABPBHKITA2020
snippet.description:
Biarpun Axiata Arena sunyi tanpa kehadiran penonton, teriakan dan tepukan gemuruh daripada kelab peminat, tetapi kehangatan Malam Kemuncak Anugerah Bintang Popular Berita Harian 33 masih terasa. Persoalan yang telah berlegar-legar di minda para peminat industri hiburan tanah air untuk berminggu lamanya bakal terjawab - Siapa paling popular?

Pilih sahaja antara platform-platform digital berikut - saluran YouTube atau Facebook TV3Malaysia, Berita Harian Online atau tontonmy, laman www.tonton.com.my atau www.abpbh.com.my, mahupun laman aplikasi TikTok TV3Malaysia - untuk menyaksikan siaran langsung ABPBH 33 mulai jam 9 malam pada 13 November.

Biarpun hanya menonton dari rumah, tetapi percayalah, sokongan anda amat dialu-alukan. Zahirkan sokongan anda secara ‘virtual’ dengan bersertakan tanda pagar #ABPBHKITA2020.

Selain para artis yang tercalon, acara ABPBH 33 turut dihangatkan lagi dengan persembahan dari Faizal Tahir, Elly Mazlein, Syamel, Zizi Kirana, Dolla, Ernie Zakri, Hafiz Suip, Azlan Typewriter, Yonnyboii, Shalma Eliana, Zynakal, Naim Daniel, Ismail Izzani, Man Keedal, Aina Abdul, Indah Ruhaila, Tomok, Lan Solo, Liza dan Azlina Aziz serta Noki K-Clique.

Datuk AC Mizal dan Nabila Huda diberi tanggungjawab mengacarakan ABPBH 33.

snippet.title: Can Trump steal the election?
snippet.description:
Republican lawsuits in the 2020 Election don’t amount to much. But the future of election law under a new US Supreme Court is a different story. 
 
Become a Video Lab member! http://bit.ly/video-lab
 
When Joe Biden won the US Presidential election, President Donald Trump threatened legal action in some of the battleground states that were among the last to count their ballots. It was all part of a campaign to cast doubt on the legality of mail-in ballots, which disproportionately favored Joe Biden. The lawsuits themselves likely won’t alter the course of the election. But one in Pennsylvania sheds light on how the current US Supreme Court might rule on future election laws.

snippet.title: 芋头的一生，辣椒…是送的The life of taro…and pepper is today’s treat丨Liziqi Channel
snippet.description:
Please  subscribe to 【李子柒 Liziqi 】Liziqi Channel on YouTube if you like my videos: https://goo.gl/nkjpSx
 #李子柒#Liziqi#ChineseCuisine #ChineseFood

小时候我爷爷教过一句让我很疑惑的顺口溜：“红薯芋头本姓张，煮的没有烧的香”…虽然到现在也想不明白为啥一定要姓“张”但一点也不妨碍我爱吃它！年初在前院大门口种了几排毛芋儿后门那多种了香芋，刚好也到了能下嘴的季节。芋儿鸡、烤芋儿、红糖芋圆蛋…你们呢？最喜欢怎么吃芋头啊？
When I was little, grandpa taught me a rather puzzling jingle: “Sweet potato and taro are surnamed Zhang, better roasted than boiled for long.” Even today I still haven’t figured out why on earth they had anything to do with the surname Zhang, but I love them anyway! At the beginning of the year, several rows of taro were planted at the gate of the front yard, and water yam at the back door. Now it’s just the time to feast on them. Taro with chicken stew, roasted taro, eggs with taro balls in brown sugar…And you? How do you like your taro best?

snippet.title: 'Don't be ridiculous': Rudy Giuliani learns about Biden win from reporters
snippet.description:
Rudy Giuliani, Donald Trump's personal attorney, was holding a press conference baselessly disputing the legitimacy of the US presidential election when news filtered through that Joe Biden had been declared the winner. 

Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

'Who was it called by?' Giuliani asked, referring to the broadcast news networks. 'All of them,' replied a reporter. The former New York City mayor insisted the result could not be called until the Trump campaign's legal challenges had gone to court.

The press conference had been called outside Four Seasons Total Landscaping, a suburban business situated between a crematorium and an adult book store on the outskirts of Philadelphia. It was unclear whether the campaign had mistaken it for the noted hotel of the same name.

US election live: Joe Biden wins and says 'It’s time for America to unite' ► https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/live/2020/nov/07/us-election-joe-biden-wins-presidency-donald-trump-kamala-harris-2020-latest-updates

snippet.title: Stuck at NIGHT in CAPE YORK! Insane Recoveries, Trackside Repairs + BEST campsite in Cape York!
snippet.description:

snippet.title: After Trump Lost Election, See How He's Losing In Court | The Beat With Ari Melber | MSNBC
snippet.description:
In a special report, MSNBC's Chief Legal Correspondent Ari Melber debunks Trump’s voter “fraud” claims with the facts and the judges’ own words from court. Melber highlights the fact that Trump's own lawyer admitted there's no evidence of voter fraud under oath and that Trump's own aides are privately acknowledging they're aware this legal fight is "unsustainable." Aired on 11/12/2020.
» Subscribe to MSNBC: http://on.msnbc.com/SubscribeTomsnbc

"The Beat" features guest interviews in addition to reporting on stories from across the country. The stories that are covered span across the political spectrum. In addition to his law background, Melber is a former Senate staffer, giving him a unique perspective to share on the political happenings coming out of Washington, D.C.

snippet.title: Can Trump steal the election?
snippet.description:
Republican lawsuits in the 2020 Election don’t amount to much. But the future of election law under a new US Supreme Court is a different story. 
 
Become a Video Lab member! http://bit.ly/video-lab
 
When Joe Biden won the US Presidential election, President Donald Trump threatened legal action in some of the battleground states that were among the last to count their ballots. It was all part of a campaign to cast doubt on the legality of mail-in ballots, which disproportionately favored Joe Biden. The lawsuits themselves likely won’t alter the course of the election. But one in Pennsylvania sheds light on how the current US Supreme Court might rule on future election laws. 

For Vox's coverage on this:

snippet.localized.title: Can Trump steal the election?
snippet.localized.description:
Republican lawsuits in the 2020 Election don’t amount to much. But the future of election law under a new US Supreme Court is a different story. 
 
Become a Video Lab member! http://bit.ly/video-lab
 
When Joe Biden won the US Presidential election, President Donald Trump threatened legal action in some of the battleground states that were among the last to count their ballots. It was all part of a campaign to cast doubt on the legality of mail-in ballots, which disproportionately favored Joe Biden. The lawsuits themselves likely won’t alter the course of the election. But one in Pennsylvania sheds light on how the current US Supreme Court might rule on future election laws.

Hello friends! Today, I return to the land of internet hauls and social media targeted recommendations - with a deep dive into the Instagram shop tab! Previously, I have bought things recommended to me via targeted ads on Facebook, Instagram, YouTube, and Snapchat - and when the shop tab was rolled out - peeking its lil head out from behind the explore page - I was instantly intrigued. So I spent an evening perusing the shop tab, finding 3 different common themes of what Instagram wanted me to buy, and then purchasing those things, and trying them out. snippet.title: CNN's Van Jones brought to tears as Joe Biden wins US election
snippet.description:
Political commentator Van Jones cried as CNN called the US election for Joe Biden. Jones said: 'It's easier to be a parent this morning ... to tell your kids character matters'. Joe Biden won the presidency by clinching Pennsylvania and its 20 electoral votes. With Biden’s victory, Kamala Harris becomes the first woman and the first person of color to become the vice-president

In and out, in and out. Staying alive is about doing things. This very second, your cells are combusting glucose molecules with oxygen to make energy available, which keeps you alive for another precious moment. To get the oxygen to your cells you are breathing.
Breathing is an answer to a very hard problem: How do you get the resources that your cells need to survive, from the outside, to the inside of your cells? Every living thing has to solve this problem and the solution is surprisingly different depending on one of the most important regulators of life: Size.

In and out, in and out. Staying alive is about doing things. This very second, your cells are combusting glucose molecules with oxygen to make energy available, which keeps you alive for another precious moment. To get the oxygen to your cells you are breathing.
Breathing is an answer to a very hard problem: How do you get the resources that your cells need to survive, from the outside, to the inside of your cells? Every living thing has to solve this problem and the solution is surprisingly different depending on one of the most important regulators of life: Size.

E agora, quem escolhe o grande finalista é você! Basta acessar www.brahma.com.br/proximon1, votar e ainda concorrer a prêmios incríveis! Bora se cadastrar porque as votações acontecem durante o programa AO VIVO. Quem sabe você não leva uma cervejeira abastecida pra casa ou um carro 0km?

O conteúdo desta live é destinado para maiores de 18 anos.

snippet.description:

Letra:
(Alok)
Pra aqueles que querem fugir da realidade
Cuidado com aquilo que te faz voar
Mas depois tira o seu céu
E o que sobra é só o inferno

(MC Hariel)
Enquanto a lata chacoalhar
E a ilusão de ser mais poderoso
Vários vai memo se arrastar
Que a Cracolândia tá lotada de curioso

(MC Davi)
Já que é pra fazer uns consciente, então fique bem ciente
Que os moleque é viciado em canetar
Vários viciou e ficou demente, só preju pros seus parentes
E a Dona Maria é crеnte e foi orar
Era o mais brabo, chapa quentе, viciou no da Tenente
Agora é dependente de droga
Molecada, pensa lá na frente antes de ser inconsequente
De ir na ideia dos outros pra usar

E eu vou passar a visão pros meus
Não precisa morrer pra falar com Deus (2x)
 
(MC Hariel)
Espera um pouco, para e pensa e controla com as droga
Que um barco sem direção, o mar leva pra rocha
A viagem é muito louca e sempre perigosa
E tá transformando em zumbi vários truta da hora
E lembra daquele parceiro que era atacante na quadra e com a mina?
Sempre avançado no tempo, pelo linguajar e pela picadilha
Dançava um break com nóis, sabadão quando tinha escola da família
Tá desandado no óleo e de bom exemplo, virou parasita
É que o beck enrolou e a brisa bateu na mente injuriada
É que a nota enrolou, ele tava na hora errada com a banca errada
Quando a brisa bateu, o convite foi feito, a atenção desviada
Prejudicou, perdeu tudo o que tinha
A família, os amigo, hoje não tem mais nada

Enquanto a lata chacoalhar
E a ilusão for a sensação de ser mais poderoso
Vários vai memo se arrastar
Que a Cracolândia tá lotada de curioso (2x)

(MC Ryan SP)
Papai, solicito socorro, me instrua
Me tire dessa rua escura
Fui dominado pela droga, desisti do ensino
Veio o apocalipse sombrear o meu caminho
Desde o início, eu já sonhava em conquistar um cargo
Currículo no Artigo 12 tava pegando mais fácil
Abandonei a linha e o pipa pelo motor da Hornet
Foi na porta do banco pelo artigo 157

E eu vou passar a visão pros meus
Não precisa morrer pra falar com Deus 
 
Enquanto a lata chacoalhar
E a ilusão de ser mais poderoso
Vários vai memo se arrastar
Que a Cracolândia tá lotada de curioso

(Salvador da Rima)
Eu vi de perto toda a adrenalina
Eu vi os corre, eu vi os mano, eu vi as mina em cima
As peça, as droga, as festa, os baile
O desespero da sua família
A necessidade fez o menor se envolver
Com treze começou a usar, com quinze a vender
Não tem nada a perder, então vai parar pra quê?
Dezoito ano, 157, preso sem viver
Amigo de copo tem um monte, pode pá
Vários amigão pra chamar pra errar
Poucos desses são os que vão te ajudar
Amigo memo é sua mãe que vai te visitar
Imagina o mundão mil grau e você aí privado
Falando com seus parentes através de carta
Cê ia ver se é fechamento quem tá do seu lado
E aprender que a liberdade se troca por nada
Essa eu fiz pra molecada que tá na ilusão
Que deixou de correr pro sonho pra correr pro crime
Cadeia não é mamão e o crime não é bombom
Então usa a mente pro certo que a vida não é filme
Essa eu fiz pra molecada que tá na ilusão
Que deixou de correr pro sonho pra correr pro crime
Cadeia não é mamão e o crime não é bombom
Então usa a mente pro certo que a vida não é filme, certo?
 
(MC Hariel)

E a ilusão for a sensação de ser mais poderoso

Que a Cracolândia tá lotada de curioso (2x)

(Alok)
[...] que querem desistir da vida
Porque não esperam mais nada dela
Talvez seja ela que espera algo de você

snippet.title: Como Sabemos que Matéria Escura Existe?
snippet.description:
Galáxias não deveriam existir. Pelo menos não se contarmos apenas a matéria visível, como as estrelas. O que vemos na prática é que todas as galáxias e a maior parte do Universo parecem ser formadas por uma substância que não emite luz, mas interage gravitacionalmente: a matéria escura. Como que podemos saber da existência de algo invisível?

snippet.title: SURPRESAS PARA O ALÊ | ANA HICKMANN
snippet.description:
Olá, pessoal! Tudo bem? Semana passada foi aniversário do Alê e eu preparei várias surpresas durante o dia pra comemorar, e hoje eu vou mostrar tudo para vocês aqui no canal. Desde o café da manhã até a pizzada no jantar, fiz tudo com muito carinho e amor para surpreender meu super marido. E é claro que não poderia faltar aquela bagunça da família durante a festa, mas é assim que a gente se diverte! Feliz aniversário de novo, meu amor! E que venham mais muitos e muitos anos de vida e dessa nossa parceria ❤️

E aí, gostaram da festa? Então não esqueçam de comentar aqui embaixo, de deixar bastante like e de se inscrever no canal. Beijão

snippet.title: Enaldinho Vs. Mussoumano - Batalha de Youtubers [Revanche]
snippet.description:
Ouça o álbum "Dupla Personalidade" completo: https://ps.onerpm.com/duplapersonalidade

Assista as NOVAS BATALHAS: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aOtP-drbd7A&list=PLj_r6fchQfwYRhfFSpRJ6MlvateXHksQ2

• contato profissional e parcerias: contato@mussoumano.com.br
• Siga nas outras redes @mussoumano

Mas o que é a Batalha de Youtubers?

Ironia, criatividade, humor ácido e muitas gargalhadas é que você pode esperar da “Batalha de Youtubers” o duelo musical mais louco do Youtube.  O rapper e youtuber Mussoumano, desafia famosos, influenciadores e celebridades para uma batalha de rap e o resultado é surpreendente. Atualmente a batalha é uma das séries da internet com maior número de visualizações, alguns dos episódios ultrapassam a marca de 20 milhões de views.  Em 2020, a série ganha nova temporada, muito mais irreverente, com novos artistas e claro, mais irônica do que nunca.

• contato profissional e parcerias: contato@mussoumano.com.br
• Siga nas outras redes @mussoumano

Mas o que é a Batalha de Youtubers?

Ironia, criatividade, humor ácido e muitas gargalhadas é que você pode esperar da “Batalha de Youtubers” o duelo musical mais louco do Youtube.  O rapper e youtuber Mussoumano, desafia famosos, influenciadores e celebridades para uma batalha de rap e o resultado é surpreendente. Atualmente a batalha é uma das séries da internet com maior número de visualizações, alguns dos episódios ultrapassam a marca de 20 milhões de views.  Em 2020, a série ganha nova temporada, muito mais irreverente, com novos artistas e claro, mais irônica do que nunca.

#BatalhaDeYoutubers #Brancoala #Mussoumano

snippet.title: Gruppenerster: DFB-Sieg nach Rückstand | Deutschland – Ukraine 3:1 | UEFA Nations League - ZDF
snippet.description:
Die deutsche Fußball-Nationalmannschaft hat auch das zweite #NationsLeague-Duell gegen die Ukraine für sich entschieden.

Früh im Spiel gingen die durch mehrere positive Corona-Tests dezimierten Ukrainer mit einem Tor von Yaremchuk (12.) mit 0:1 in Führung und blieben die erste Halbzeit lang durch Konter gefährlich. Durch eine Einzelaktion von Leroy Sané, der nach einem Haken vom Strafraumrand abzog, glich das DFB-Team in der 23. Minute aus. Nur zehn Minuten später dann die Führung für #Deutschland. Nach dem zweiten Assist von Leon Goretzka köpfte Timo Werner den Ball zum 2:1 Halbzeitstand ins Tor. In der zweiten Halbzeit zeigten sich die Ukrainer offensiver, was Werner in der 64. Minute zu seinem Doppelpack und dem 3:1 Endstand nutzte. In der Schlussphase trafen die Gäste doppelt den Pfosten (75., 82.), während ein Kopfball von Goretzka (81.) leicht von Ukraine-Keeper Pyatov abgewehrt werden konnte.

Auch im fünften Spiel in der Nations League blieb die deutsche Mannschaft nicht ohne Gegentreffer. Das deutsche Team musste auf den gesperrten Kroos und den verletzten Kimmich verzichten. Keeper Neuer zog mit seinem 95. Länderspieleinsatz mit DFB-Rekordtorhüter Sepp Maier gleich.

Weitere Sportvideos gibt es bei #ZDFsport https://www.zdf.de/sport#xtor=CS3-72

ZDFsport abonnieren? Hier klicken http://kurz.zdf.de/sportabo/
ZDFsport bei Facebook https://de-de.facebook.com/ZDFsport/
ZDFsport bei Instagram https://www.instagram.com/zdfsport/

Gespielt hat Deutschland gegen die Ukraine in der Red-Bull-Arena in Leipzig. Aufgrund der Corona-Beschränkungen durften keine Zuschauer ins Stadion kommen. Mit dem Sieg steht Deutschland in der Tabelle der Gruppe A4 der UEFA Nations League 2020/21 auf Platz 1 vor Spanien, das gegen die Schweiz nur ein 1:1 Remis holte. Am Dienstag treffen die beiden Teams direkt aufeinander. Dem DFB-Team reicht ein Unentschieden zum Gruppensieg.

Die Mannschaften aus Deutschland und der Ukraine gingen mit den folgenden Aufstellungen an den Start: 

Deutschland (DFB-Team, Die Mannschaft)

Neuer (Bayern München/34 Jahre alt/95 Länderspiele) – Koch (Leeds United/24/6), Ginter (Bor. Mönchengladbach/26/34), Max (PSV Eindhoven/27/2), Süle (Bayern München/25/28), Rüdiger (FC Chelsea/27/37) – Goretzka (Bayern München/25/28), Gündogan (Manchester City/30/41) – Gnabry (Bayern München/25/16), Sané (Bayern München/24/24) , Werner (FC Chelsea/24/34)
Trainer: Joachim Löw

Ukraine

Pyatov (Schachtjor Donezk/36/96) – Sobol (FC Brügge/25/18), Zabarnyi (Dynamo Kiew/18/4), Konoplia (Desna Chernihiv/21/3), Matviyenko (Schachtjor Donezk/24/30) – Stepanenko (Schachtjor Donezk/31/59), Malinovskyi (Atalanta Bergamo/27/32), Zinchenko (Manchester City/23/35)  – Yaremchuk (KAA Gent/24/19), Marlos (Schachtjor Donezk/32/21), Zubkov (Ferencvarosi TC/24/5)
Trainer: Andriy Shevchenko

snippet.title: Lockdown-Update #2 - Wunderland im Ausnahmezustand
snippet.description:
Lockdown im Wunderland. Wir nutzen die Zeit für Projekte, die wir schon immer umsetzen wollten, wenn keine Besucher da sind. Wir erneuern derzeit die Start- und Landebahn unseres Flughafens. Dafür werden 32 Platten, 1000 LEDs, 1500 Wiederstände, 1000 m Kabel und 50 Carsystem-Verbraucher ausgetauscht. Gerrit und sein Team bestücken die gefräste Nut mit den magnetischen Fahrband. In der letzen Woche haben wir den Fußboden rausgerissen. Nun haben wir die Ausgleichmasse gegossen und den neuen Boden verlegt.

snippet.title: Yoga Hüftöffner für Entspannung & Beweglichkeit | Intensive Dehnung für  flexible Hüften | 25 Min.
snippet.description:
Heute erwartet euch eine feine Yoga-Hüftöffner-Sequenz, die euch dabei unterstützt euer Hüftgelenk zu mobilisieren und somit eure Hüfte geschmeidig und beweglich zu halten. Die Übungen in der heutigen Einheit helfen euch aber nicht nur flexibler zu werden, sondern können auch bei Schmerzen im unteren Rücken entlastend wirken.

Aus yogischer Sicht spricht man davon, dass Emotionen & Anspannungen in unseren Hüften gespeichert werden. Hüftöffner können also auch dabei unterstützen sich diese Gefühle bewusst zu machen und emotionale Blockaden zu lösen.

Diese Einheit richtet sich eher an Teilnehmer*innen, die bereits Yoga praktiziert haben, da ich nicht jede einzelne Asana im Detail erkläre.
Sollten euch Übungen zu intensiv sein, bitte kommt wieder raus! Zwingt euren Körper bitte nicht in Positionen, die sich eng und möglicherweise schmerzhaft anfühlen.

Sollte die Halbe Taube zu intensiv sein, praktiziert bitte alternativ das „Nadelöhr“ (Rückenlage, Fuß geflext auf Knie, Schienbein oder Oberschenkel ranziehen)

Als Hilfsmittel schnappt euch gerne eine dicke Decke um eure Knie zu polstern und euch eventuell in der halben Taube zu unterstützen.

Diese Sequenz eignet sich ganz prima allein für sich, als auch als Ergänzung zu einer kraftvollen Praxis.

snippet.title: CLAN WARS 2 IMPROVEMENTS & FIXES! 🛠️ Clash Royale Update TV Royale
snippet.description:
We heard your Clan Wars 2 feedback! We're adding a number of new changes and improvements to the Clan Wars experience in our next update. Follow Drew on Twitter: https://twitter.com/drewbian
Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

00:00 TIME ZONE ISSUE
00:47 PARTICPATION CAP
01:05 CLAN MATCHMAKING
01:44 NEW RIVER LENGTHS
02:07 FAME BOOST
02:21 GAME MODES
02:31 NEW LEGENDARY LEAGUES
02:47 CLAN UI CHANGES
03:22 NEW MINIMUM MEMBER CAP
03:36 SUPERCELL ID FRIENDS
03:57 OTHER FIXES & IMPROVEMENTS

Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more.

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

Lead the Clash Royale Family to victory!

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent's Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: Folge 5.3 – FREUDE oder TRÄNEN? Lea sieht Zimmer zum ersten Mal | MACH MAL mit OBI
snippet.description:
Hier gibt es alle Anleitungen: https://www.obi.de/machmal 
Endlich darf auch Lea ihr neues Zimmer sehen! Moritz hat das Zimmer seiner Schwester ordentlich auf den Kopf gestellt und gemeinsam mit Julia einen Schminktisch, eine Chill-Ecke oder auch den Käfig von Leas Hamster umgebaut. Die wichtigste Frage ist aber: Wie wird Lea ihr neues Zimmer gefallen? Was würdest du am Liebsten in deinem Zimmer umbauen? Schreib es uns in die Kommentare!

Lust die coolen DIYs von Julia und Moritz oder andere tolle Preise zu gewinnen? Dann werde jetzt selber kreativ und schick uns dein DIY-Video (max. 20 Sekunden) und eine unterschriebene Einverständniserklärung per Mail an machmalmit@obi.de. Die Erklärung schicken wir Dir zu, wenn Du Dich mit Deinem Video an uns wendest. 
Wenn du TikTok hast, zeig dein Werk auch gerne der Welt und tagge dein Video mit #machmalmitobi. 

Mach Mal mit OBI! Jeden Montag, Mittwoch und Freitag um 16:00 Uhr zeigen dir HeyMoritz und Julia Beautx coole Ideen zum Selbermachen!
--------------------
▶ Abonniere uns: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCofdO6pnChnoTvyvm0niAKQ?sub_confirmation=1

snippet.title: Ruhe Agrar Teil 5: Der neue Standort Picher - Mähdrusch & Bodenbearbeitung [Massey Ferguson Technik]
snippet.description:
Der Landwirtschaftsbetrieb Ruhe Agrar bewirtschaftet mehrere tausend Hektar Agrarflächen in Nord- und Ostdeutschland. Das Hauptbetätigungsfeld des Agrarbetriebs ist die Produktion von erneuerbarer Energie aus Biomasse. In dieser mehrteiligen Kurzfilmreihe besuchen wir alle Standorte und werfen einen Blick auf die wichtigen Feldarbeiten. In Teil 5 nehmen wir euch mit auf den neuen Standort am Dorfrand von Picher in Mecklenburg-Vorpommern. Hier hat Ende Juli 2020 bereits die Getreideernte begonnen und die Bodenbearbeitung läuft. Im Einsatz zu sehen sind Traktoren und Mähdrescher von Massey Ferguson. Außerdem zeigen wir Eindrücke des neuen Betriebsgeländes. Viel Spaß!

snippet.title: Das beste BURGER BUN Rezept. Punkt! Brioche Burger Buns selber machen
snippet.description:
Mach deinen Burger zu etwas besonderem! Die besten Brioche Burger Buns die du je gemacht hast, sind nur ein kleines Rezept von dir entfernt. Es gibt sogar zwei Rezepte für die perfekten Buger Buns. 
Nicht vergessen: Burgerbrötchen selber machen ist keine Wissenschaft :) Viel Spaß bei den kein Stress kochen Burger Buns.

Rezept "simple" Brioche Burger Buns:
500g Mehl (Type 550 oder glattes W700, mind 12g Eiweiß!)
250 ml Milch (oder Wasser wenn die Zeiten hart sind) 
1 Ei plus eines zum bestreichen 
1 Pkg Trockenhefe
3/4 EL Salz
2 EL Zucker
2 EL Butter

DAS BESTE Brioche Burger Bun Rezept:
375g Mehl (Type 550 oder glattes W700, mind 12g Eiweiß!)
40g Zucker
10g Salz
1 Pkg Trockenhefe
75g Milch
100g Butter
170g Ei (ca. 3 Stück M)
Plus ein Ei zum bestreichen 

#burgerbuns #homemadeburger #burger

snippet.title: Der Weidemann für einen Rollstuhlfahrer | landwirt.com
snippet.description:
Kevin und seine Frau Verena betreiben einen landwirtschaftlichen Betrieb mit Direktvermarktung in Niederösterreich. Kevin sitzt seit einem Unfall im Rollstuhl. Ein Schicksalsschlag, der sein Leben verändert hat. Doch für ihn war klar, dass dieses Handicap ihn nicht davon abhalten wird, seinen Traum als Landwirt weiter zu verfolgen. Schnell war klar, dass er eine Maschine braucht, die ihm die Arbeit erleichtert und mit der er alle Tätigkeiten am Hof alleine meistern kann. Die Anschaffung eines Teleskopladers stand bevor. Das Team von MAUCH hat einen Weidemann T4108 so angepasst, sodass er seinen Anforderungen voll und ganz entspricht.

snippet.description:
In der zweiten Runde der 8. Staffel "Das große Backen" schicken wir unsere Hobbybäcker auf eine köstliche Reise durch das wunderschöne Frankreich. Das Ursprungsland der Patisserié hält drei knifflige Aufgaben für die Kandidaten bereit. Wer kann dem Druck standhalten und wer muss diese Woche leider das Backzelt verlassen?

#DasGroßeBacken #SAT1

Bei „Das große Backen“ sucht SAT.1 wieder „Deutschlands besten Hobbybäcker“: Zehn Kandidaten aus ganz Deutschland stellen sich der Jury! Die Juroren Christian Hümbs, mehrfach ausgezeichnet als Patissier des Jahres, und Bettina Schliephake-Burchardt, Konditormeisterin und gefeierte Tortendekorateurin erwarten von den zehn Kandidaten vor allem eines: absolute Höchstleistungen. Dem Gewinner winken ein eigenes Backbuch und 10.000 Euro Preisgeld. 

Auch die Moderatorin ist Fans der Koch-Show bereits bekannt: Enie van de Meiklokjes. Die leidenschaftliche Hobbybäckerin führt bereits seit Staffel 1 durch die Sendung.

snippet.title: Spätes Drama! Szoboszlai knallt Ungarn in deutsche EM-Gruppe: Ungarn - Island 2:1 | EM-Quali | DAZN
snippet.description:
Ungarn entreißt Island durch einen späten Doppelschlag das EM-Ticket. Nach einem dicken Patzer von RB-Keeper Peter Gulacsi gingen die Nordeuropäer durch Gylfi Sigurdssons Freistoß in Führung. In den finalen Minuten drehte Ungarn durch Loic Nego (88. Minute) und einem schönen Fernschuss von Dominik Szoboszlai in der Nachspielzeit diese Partie. Die Ungarn treffen bei der Europameisterschaft 2021 in der Gruppenphase auf Deutschland.
